          Native iOS and Android apps. Full feature parity with the web experience.
        </mc-text>
      </mc-column>
    </mc-section>

    <!-- ═══ PRODUCT SHOWCASE — 2 COLUMN ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <mc-section class="bg-slate-800 px-8 py-16">
